  "blocks": [
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "id": "p0065.b004",
      "children": [
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Example: ",
          "marks": [
            "bold",
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Knockback to the left. Specific Knockback direction  ",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "overrides regular rules.",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "id": "p0065.b001",
      "children": [
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Knockdown:",
          "marks": [
            "bold"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " Gain the ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Knockdown",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " Condition card, ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Falling down ",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "side up, and place your miniature on the side. Follow the rules of ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "the Condition card. If Knockdown is caused by an Attack, it affects ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "the Target only if it is within the Primordial\u2019s effective range (ad-",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " jacent for Melee Attacks, in the designated zone for Zone Attacks, ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "within X spaces for Ranged X Attacks, etc.). If it\u2019s caused by a Re-",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " sponse, it affects the Attacker only if they are within adjacency.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "id": "p0065.b002",
      "children": [
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Knockdown is a special Condition. When you get knocked down, ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "you put your miniature on its side and take a ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Knockdown (falling ",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "down)",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " card. While you have the ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Knockdown (falling down) ",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "card, ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "you cannot perform any actions, reactions or free actions, unless ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "stated otherwise. At the end of your next turn, you flip the card to ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "the ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Knockdown (standing up)",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " side. All Titans with a ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Knockdown",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " (standing up) ",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "card stand up at the start of their next turn. If for ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "whatever reason this card is discarded, stand up too.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "id": "p0065.b006",
      "children": [
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Example:",
          "marks": [
            "bold",
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " Knockback 4 to the left. When a Titan is knocked back  ",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "into another Titan, the other Titan is displaced (according  ",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "to involuntary movement rules).",
          "marks": [
            "italic"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
